10:
Judah also marched against the Canaanites who were living in Hebron
 (Hebron was formerly named Kiriath-arba
). They struck down Sheshai, Ahiman, and Talmai.

24:
Most blessed of women is Jael,
the wife of Heber the Kenite;
she is most blessed among tent-dwelling women.

27:
He collapsed, he fell, he lay down between her feet;
he collapsed, he fell between her feet;
where he collapsed, there he fell — dead.

